title: Don't Be a Donkey
itunes:title: Don't Be a Donkey
description:
Episode 238 - Have trouble making decisions? You can do almost anything that you want in this life, you just can't do it all at once. It's about figuring out what is next and then executing. Don't try to do multiple things at once. Don't have a Plan B. Just make a decision and execute.
